      <outline text="Note it! Interview and review of a very functional widget!">
        <outline text="This widget is awesome, now you can actually use the note function in your ipod on a daily basis. This widget sends text notes to your cell phone and or your ipod. It is amazing, you can only set a certain length text message but the limit is very large. Its sleek, and beautiful. This widget is a great example of form following function. The interface is almost like something you would see in a cell phone or an ipod and again it just works. We give it 5 stars. Send us your comments to widgetshow@gmail.com &lt;mailto:widgetshow@gmail.com&gt;"/>
      </outline>
